track_notes: Because the road trip to the departure is a long drive, it is fine to climb another summit on the rool next to this one. The path is nice in the forest and the summit is a bit funny with a sight to the sea and corsica island!
Not the shortest path to this summit!!! You can drive on this small forest road to approach the summit. This is a nice place in the forest to walk.
You can come from La colmiane to this summit and activate Mt chalancha too.
